    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Application
    Main application entry point for the WeCel communications system.
    Asesor
    Represents an advisor in the system.
    AsesorNocreado
    Exception thrown when an advisor (Asesor) cannot be created or found in the system.
    Cliente
    Represents a client in the system.
    ClienteNocreado
    Exception thrown when a client (Cliente) cannot be created in the system.
    ContrasenaVacia
    Exception thrown when a password (contrase√±a) is empty or invalid during authentication.
    Controlador
    Controller class that acts as an intermediary between the GUI and the Service layer.
    Gui
    Graphical User Interface class that handles all user interactions through dialog boxes.
    MegasNegativas
    Exception thrown when negative or invalid megabyte values are provided for internet plans.
    MinutosGigasnegativos
    Exception thrown when negative or invalid values are provided for minutes or gigabytes in mobile plans.
    NoExistePlan
    Exception thrown when attempting to access or reference a plan that does not exist in the system.
    Peticion
    Represents a Petition type of PQRS.
    Plan
    Abstract base class representing a service plan in the system.
    PlanHogar
    Represents a home service plan.
    PlanMovil
    Represents a mobile service plan.
    PQRS
    Abstract base class representing a PQRS (Petition, Complaint, Claim, Suggestion) in the system.
    PQRSNoEncontrada
    Exception thrown when a PQRS record cannot be found in the system.
    Queja
    Represents a Complaint (Queja) type of PQRS.
    Reclamo
    Represents a Claim (Reclamo) type of PQRS.
    Servicios
    Service class that handles the business logic for the telecommunications company system.
    Sugerencia
    Represents a Suggestion (Sugerencia) type of PQRS.
    TipoTVincorrectos
    Exception thrown when an invalid TV type is specified for home plans.
    Usuario
    Represents a user in the system.
    UsuarioNoencontrado
    Exception thrown when a user cannot be found in the system.
